1. *Učitelju*, molim te da mi pomogneš da razumem ovaj zadatak. (Teacher, please help me understand this task.)
2. Ja sam *učitelj* engleskog jezika. (I am an English language teacher.)
3. *Učitelju*, šta misliš o ovom predlogu? (Teacher, what do you think about this proposal?)
4. Moja majka je *učiteljica* u osnovnoj školi. (My mother is a primary school teacher.)
5. Kada sam bio mali, *učitelj* mi je govorio da čitam svaki dan. (When I was little, my teacher told me to read every day.)
6. Moja sestra je *učiteljka* baleta. (My sister is a ballet teacher.)
7. *Učiteljima* je potrebno dati veću platu za njihov trud i rad. (Teachers need to be given a higher salary for their effort and work.)
8. *Učitelj* je dao dobar savet svom učeniku pre testa. (The teacher gave good advice to his student before the test.)
9. Kada sam bio u školi, *učitelji* su nas učili da budemo dobri ljudi. (When I was in school, teachers taught us to be good people.)
10. Moja baka je bila *učitelj* u penziji. (My grandmother was a retired teacher.)